 Former Spice Girl Geri Halliwell is to marry Formula One team principal Christian Horner / An ad was placed by the loved-up pair in the Times today. Under ‘Forthcoming Marriages’, a notice headlined ‘Mr C.E.J. Horner OBE And Miss G.E. Halliwell’ appeared. “The engagement is announced between Christian, son of Mr and Mrs G.M. Horner and Geraldine, daughter of the late Mr L.F. Halliwell and Mrs A. Parkinson,” the notice read.  The newspaper method of announcing of a marriage comes less than a week after Sherlock star Benedict Cumberbatch announced he was to wed Sophie Hunter in the same publication. 
